Titolo: Covenant of Solitude

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Covenant of Solitude is a role-playing game published by Kemco for Android and iOS devices. It is considered one of Kemco's best-looking video games, although the soundtrack and audio were not well received.The game is a turn-based RPG, where players assume the role of Fort, a boy feared by his village for his "genie" blood. This blood grants Fort the power to summon and control "monsters" which serve as the primary allies and enemies within the game. The story involves an expansionist Empire and a struggle for control over Fort's power.

